  "subject": "Enforcing rules for Maven projects",
  "commit_message": "Enforcing rules for Maven projects\n\nAutomatically enforcing below rules for Maven projects using maven enforcer plugin\nMake sure *-core modules in dependencies do not have compile/provided scope\nMake sure testng and junit Maven dependencies have test scope\n3rd-party infrastructure dependency must have scope \"provided\"\n\nChange-Id: I80665f2abde2f8514976f639724b11aecbb2c4a8\nIssue-ID: SDC-1065\nSigned-off-by: sheetalm <sheetal.mudholkar@amdocs.com>\n",
